## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not encompass the full spectrum of perspectives on the role of art in life. Additionally, the subjective nature of art means that its impact can vary significantly among individuals. Further research could explore a broader range of cultural contexts and artistic disciplines to provide a more comprehensive understanding.

